-- Anheuser-Busch Says Arbitration Panel Confirms Stance on Modelo Agreement
-- Rebecca Evans
-- 2010-07-12T04:15:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/anheuser-busch-says-arbitration-panel-confirms-stance-on-modelo-agreement.html

          
          
             Anheuser-Busch InBev NV said an
arbitration panel ruled that the combination of Anheuser-
Busch and InBev did not violate the investment agreement between
entities of Anheuser-Busch and Grupo Modelo SAB.  
 The company reported the information in an e-mailed
statement today.  
          
          


  


        